00:02:55,638 --> 00:02:59,562
is a missed opportunity for indie developers.

51
00:02:59,562 --> 00:03:00,763
For us, it was a practical tool.

52
00:03:00,763 --> 00:03:04,086
It was something that we consulted and referred to

