00:04:29,572 --> 00:04:32,493
And so we invested early and intensely

80
00:04:32,493 --> 00:04:36,295
in clearly understanding the game's creative direction.

81
00:04:36,295 --> 00:04:40,017
And we looked back on it at every sort of decision point.

82
00:04:41,729 --> 00:04:45,471
