all sort of like, all the features funnel in together

86
00:04:51,253 --> 00:04:53,754
to deliver this sort of singular experience.

87
00:04:53,754 --> 00:04:55,655
And that's great, but it wasn't by accident.

88
00:04:55,655 --> 00:04:59,537
It was basically a function of how we approached

