00:05:32,824 --> 00:05:34,565
framework for you to move forward.

98
00:05:34,565 --> 00:05:36,967
And from that trunk, the branches grow out,

99
00:05:36,967 --> 00:05:38,207
all the different disciplines.

100
00:05:38,207 --> 00:05:39,768
So design can head off in its area

